data.description: Discover the charm of this East South Shore residence! A 4-bed, 2-bath haven with a bonus room in the finished basement, this home underwent a 2019 renovation. Revel in modern comforts, including a new roof, upgraded plumbing, electrical, and AC. The cozy backyard is an ideal space for gatherings and relaxation.  Just minutes from Lake Shore Drive, and in close proximity to dining, parks, and the new Obama Library. Perfect for commuters with easy access to major routes. Seize the opportunity! Schedule your showing today to envision the lifestyle this home offers. ***Ask me about our forgivable grants up to $10,000 coupled with below market rates and discounted mortgage insurance***
